abstract: After months of boardroom wrangling, the fight over Dell may be drawing to a close. | It seems no sum is too large for companies looking to raise money through the debt markets. | New York State plans to drop out of an agreement over rules for insurers. | Henry M. headline.main: In Dell Buyout, a Final Chapter
